<item>
            <title>[OAK-7208] Various disallowed control characters are accepted in item names</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-7208</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Our node name check currently allow control characters other than CR, LF and TAB. This is a bug according to JCR, names being restricted to XML characters.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
